Compile options and module requirement
*** 
    *If using pgi compiler, load cuda/9.0.69 on summitdev
    *If using gcc compiler, load cuda/9.2.148 or default on summitdev

(1) CUDA/C++
    USE_CUDA = TRUE

(2) CUDA/OpenACC; use pgi
    USE_CUDA = TRUE
    USE_ACC  = TRUE
    USE_OMP_OFFLOAD = FALSE

(3) CUDA/OpenMP; use gcc
    USE_CUDA = TRUE
    USE_ACC  = FALSE
    USE_OMP_OFFLOAD = TRUE
